	<Title>
		Psoriasis diet: Can changing your diet treat psoriasis?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		There is no psoriasis diet, but eating healthy foods is still beneficial.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Can changing my diet treat psoriasis?
	</Question>
